\[x^{k} = \mathbf{prox}_{(1/2)f}(z^{k}),\quad y^{k}=2(z^{k}-x^{k})\] \[w^{k+1} = w^{k}-0.33(y^{k}+3w^{k})\] \[z^{k+1} = z^{k}-0.16(5y^{k}+3w^{k}).\]

